<a name="Appendix I"><hr></a>
<h3>Illinois State Data Center</h3>

The Illinois State Data Center, in conjuction with the U.S. Census Bureau,
coordinates access to and the use of statistical resources for
administration, planning and decision making in Illinois.  The State Data
Center Cooperative is a six member consortium that provides a full range of
data services to citizens, libraries, state and local government,
businesses, community leaders, university educators, planners and others.
A list of State Data Center affiliates is contained in appendix I.<p>




