-->

<br clear=all>
<p><br>
<hr>
<center><h4>The Department of Commerce and Community Affairs presents . . .</h4></center>
<center><img src="../graph/ilb&s2.gif" alt="Illinois Building & Sites Online!"></center>

<h4>
The information included in this presentation represents a sampling of the important economic development information available to you through the Department of Commerce and Community Affairs. We maintain an active and expanding information-base with hundreds of properties to help you expand or locate in our state. We can also put you in touch with local markets for information and resources targeted to your specific needs.<p>

Please visit this site regularly as we continue to enhance this service. Be sure to <a href="mailto:tom.hamrick@accessil.com">write us</a> with your comments and suggestions about information important to you.<p>

Illinois . . . A great state for business keeps getting better!<p>

<em>Dennis R. Whetstone, Director</em><p>
