Illinois is a leader in the production of:<p>
<ul type=square>
<li>construction machinery
<li>farm equipment
<li>cellular phones
<li>radio and TV sets
<li>flavoring extracts and syrups
<li>housewares
<li>nuts and bolts
<li>shortening and cooking oils
<li>metal coatings
<li>polishes and sanitation goods
<li>surgical appliances and suppliers
<li>food containers
<li>flour and grain
<li>printing machinery
<li>electric coils and transformers
<li>environmental controls
<li>confectionery products
<li>pet food
<li>commercial printing
</ul>

