<HR>
<center><img src="../../graph/gmlogo.gif" width=544 height=146></center>
<CENTER><H2>Spring, 1996</H2></CENTER>
<h5 align=center>A Newsletter for CDAP Grantees from the Illinois Department of Commerce and Community Affairs</h5>
<hr>
<p>
<h3>IN THIS ISSUE</h3>
<h4><ul type=square>
<li>      <a href="#Intro">Introduction</a>
<li>      <a href="#Program Changes">1996 Program Changes</a>
<li>      <a href="#CDAP Funded Contracts">CDAP Funded Contracts - Requests for Payroll Information	</a>
<li>      <a href="#Implementing Section 3 Report Req">Implementing Section 3 Reporting Requirements  </a>
