specialist at the NAFTA Opportunity Center at Bradley University
in Peoria, on her recent wedding.<p>

Congratulations to Doug Harlan, director of the Procurement
Technical Assistance Center at Cooperative Extension Service in
Decatur, and his wife on the birth of their second child. It's a
girl!<p>

