There are two other documents available from the Agency that are similar 
in format to this document.<p>

Does Your Business Need an Air Pollution Control Permit?<p>

Does Your Business Need a Water Pollution Control Permit?<p>

You may obtain copies of either document or additional copies of this document, by contacting the Office of Small Business or by contacting the appropriate permit section.<p>

<ul>
Office of Small Business -- 217/524-2743<p>
Bureau of Air Permit Section -- 217/782-2113<p>
Bureau of Land Permit Section -- 217/524-3300<p>
Bureau of Water Permit Section -- 217/782-0610<p>
</ul>

You may also obtain information or assistance from these sections by calling the above numbers.<p>


