<CENTER><H3>Program Overview</H3></CENTER>
<HR>
<H4>
DCCA maintains a full-time staff of international business experts in
its Chicago office; six foreign trade offices located in Brussels,
Tokyo, Hong Kong, Mexico City, Warsaw and Budapest; and a network of
five International Trade Centers located throughout Illinois to help
Illinois businesses begin exporting or gain entry to new world
markets.  These experts also work with foreign-owned businesses to
help them find locations in Illinois.<P>

For information call 312/814-7164.<P>
</H4>


