<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA - International Trade Assistance</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#8080C0" ALINK="#8080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<h3>
Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p>
</h3>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<font size=+3>International Business Division</font>
<br clear=right>
<hr>


<CENTER><H3>ExPro - Trade Lead Matches</H3></CENTER>
<HR>

In order to provide Illinois companies with an improved system to receive international trade leads, DCCA's IBD has implemented a new technologically proficient system known as "ExPro" (Export Promotion Trade Management System).  ExPro is designed to facilitate the matching of companies with trade leads in order to deliver fresh leads in a more timely manner.<P>

Companies interested in this free service may request a Company Background Sheet form from the Department of Commerce and Community Affairs - International Business Division.  After the form has been completed, it may be returned, via fax or mail, to our office.  The form will require companies to provide their 6 digit Harmonized System (H.S. or Schedule B) Codes and their 4 digit SIC Codes for each product.  A foreign trade lead, specific to your industry, can then be matched and faxed directly to the company.  Harmonized System Codes may be obtained from either your company's shipping department, a freight forwarder/custom broker, or you can contact the U.S. Department of Commerce at 301/763-5200 or fax to 301/763-1109.<P>

Company specific information will be entered into our database and your company will be notified via fax of any trade lead matches as they occur. Our database is uploaded weekly via a computer clearinghouse to insure access to the most current trade lead information possible.  If you wish to participate in this program, please call DCCA's International Business Division at 312/814-7164; TDD, 312/419-0667, or send your request via fax to 312/814-6581, Attention: ExPro - Guang Yang.<P>


<HR>
<STRONG>| <A HREF="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</A> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/asstprog.htm">Business Assistance</A> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/ibdiv.htm"> International Business</A> |</STRONG>
</BODY>
