<strong><em>Medication</em></strong> - Repeal replaced by above.<p>

<strong><em>PPT</em></strong> - Establishes a PPT wager which combines two perfectas and one trifecta into a single wager.  (New)<p>

<hr>
<h4>DEPARTMENT OF REHABILITATION SERVICES</h4>

<strong><em>Customer Financial Participation</em></strong> - Revises customer financial participation of the cost of the vocational rehab services.  Makes the Standard Budget Allowances and rate of participation more fair and equitable for all individuals seeking services.  Parental participation has been revised to match the federal guidelines for student financial assistance. <p>

