<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Consumer Credit Counseling License</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.  Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<dl><dd>
Consumer Credit Counseling License
</dd></dl><HR>
<H3>II.  Agency:</H3>
<dl><dd>
Department of Financial Institutions<BR>
Consumer Credit Division<BR>
500 Iles Park Place, Suite 500<BR>
Springfield, IL 62718<BR>
(217) 782-3704<BR>
</dd></dl><hr>

<H3>III.  Statute:</H3>
<dl><dd>
805 Illinois Compiled Statutes 140 
</dd></dl><HR>

<H3>IV. Requirement Description:
</H3>
<dl><dd>
Not-for-profit corporations may organize under the Consumer Credit Counseling Corporation Act to provide specialized personal and group counseling services to the members of the general public who suffer economic hardship due to the extended credit beyond their ability to repay on a regular schedule.  Those corporations may act as agent for such individuals to resolve their economic difficulties. A separate license is required for each business. Operating without a  license is a business offense subject to a file of up to $500. Licenses are valid for one year and expire every December 31. <P>

Renewal applications and fees must be submitted to the Department by December 15.  <P></dd></dl><hr>

<H3>V. Approval Process:</H3>
<dl><dd>
Applications must include a credit report and financial statements for each business location.<P>

Applications are usually processed in 30 days.  <P> 
</dd></dl><hr>

<H3>VI. Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post Requisites:
</H3><dl><dd>
License holders are subject to examination by the Department at its discretion.
</dd></dl><hr>

<H3>VII. Fees:</H3>
<dl><dd>
Annual License Fee:   $100    <BR>   Initial Investigation Fee: $35  <BR>
Relocation Fee:       $ 10    <BR>   Name Change:               $10  <BR>
</dd></dl>








