<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Illinois Wage Payment and Collection Act  </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.	Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Wage Payment and Collection Act  
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>II.	Agency:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Department of Labor<BR>
Fair Labor Standards Division<BR>
160 North La Salle St. C-1300<BR>
Chicago, IL 60601<BR>
(312) 793-2808<BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>III.	Statute:</H3>
<DL><DD>
820 Illinois Compiled Statutes 115
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>IV. 	Requirement Description:</H3>
<DL><DD>
This Act  requires employers to pay employee wages and final compensation within a prescribed number of days following the pay period in which they were earned. The Department can assist employees in the collection of wages or final compensation due them. The law applies to all employers doing business in the State of Illinois, except State and Federal governments, and prohibits the deductions from wages or final compensation (except as specified in the Law). Underpayment or the refusal to pay 	wages, or the false denial of the amount or validity of wages due is a Class C misdemeanor and each day during which a violation of the Act continues is a separate offense. Failure to 	pay wages in 15 days after an order by the Department may result in a penalty of 1% per calendar day to the employee (up to twice the amount due the employee).<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>V.	Approval Process:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VI.	Pre- Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VII.	Fees:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>


<HR>
<STRONG>| <a href="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsm1.htm">First Stop</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsbr.htm">Business Requirements</a> |</STRONG>

